Time is an entity that waits for none. Fleeting moments carry with them the imprints of sweet memories that make their way into our minds or wither away into oblivion. Sometimes during a moment of gloom sight of our timepieces can bring back memories lying hidden in some corner of our heart and make our existence worthwhile. Watches have undergone radical transformation over time; from sands of time encased in vessels timekeeping devices have metamorphosed into wristwatches. From being items of necessity watches have become luxurious commodities serving multiple functions.

Donna Karan New York a U.S. based fashion house has been in the business of watch making for decades and has been satisfying their fans across the globe with an assortment of timepieces that boast of sleek design and efficient performance. This particular analog watch is the ideal fashion accessory that will make your appearance more glamorous and elegant. This DKNY analog watch is crafted for women who love to flaunt their style. The pace of timekeeping mechanism in this marvelous timepiece is set by the electro-oscillations of a quartz crystal present inside the watch.

Body and Design

This watch from DKNY bears the unique touch of craftsmanship that sets this watchmaker company apart from the rest. Attractive opulence and the brilliant sheen that this timepiece boasts of will succeed in drawing the attention of all and sundry in any social gathering. Be prepared to be showered with praises for your refined taste courtesy of this dazzling timeframe. Built in an unorthodox style the round dial sports glittery hands and classy timestamps in the form of bars. The beauty of this classy timepiece is accentuated by a mineral glass window on the dial which has a diameter of 30 mm. The glass cover also protects the sensitive components of the dial from scratches thanks to its sturdiness.

One of the most striking features of this glittery watch is the stainless steel bezel. Timekeeping is stylishly redefined by the crystallised bezel which is encrusted with shiny stones making the timepiece even more alluring. The radiance of the bezel is matched by an equally beautiful case. The watch case is made of stainless steel making you look gorgeous. Apart from its polished look stainless steel is also sturdy and wear resistant. Thanks to its property of being temperature resistant stainless steel helps the watch case survive in all seasons. The stainless steel case is resistant to corrosion thus making this watch more durable.

This analog watch from DKNY is equipped with a ceramic strap which makes the timepiece a comfortable wear. Ceramic is lightweight and sturdy hence the bracelet can withstand the pressures of daily use. The strap comes as a boon to those who have a sensitive skin because prolonged use of this watch will never cause any irritation to the wearer courtesy of ceramic. To further add to your comfort the watch is endowed with push button clasp. This makes sure that no matter under what conditions you wear your favourite timeframe; it will always remain glued to your wrist.

Functions and Other Features

If you are planning to go on a picnic with your family and friends do not forget to carry this watch along. This designer timepiece is water resistant up to a depth of 50 m so you can wear this watch as you swim in a stream during the picnic trip or have a fun fishing expedition. Your precious timepiece will also remain unharmed even if you get wet in the rains. This smart device also possesses a luminous glow that helps you in viewing the time in pitch dark conditions. This charming timepiece is crafted for delivering efficiency in style.
